#ShePersisted: Betsy DeVos On Protesters, “I Will Not Be Deterred”
Posted at 2:15 pm on February 10, 2017 by Mickey White

Share On Facebook Share On Twitter

 
 
Secretary of Education, Betsy DeVos has issued a statement about her encounter with liberal lunatic protesters, Friday morning. The protesters prevented her from entering the school through one door, so she used another. I have to give her credit, she is considerably more professional than I would have been about the whole thing…



 
